structure.unit: TRAFFIC REGULATIONS -- VEHICLE EQUIPMENT AND STORAGE

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 115, par. 1; amended 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 176, sec. 5. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 5, secs. 2, 5, and 8. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2739g-83 to 2739g-85.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: height, width and length of trucks and semitrailer trucks.
